{"tid":1293094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長期抗爭：全港各區齊齊向外地遊客輸出軟實力","createTime":"2019-07-07T14:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:42:33.000Z","uid":270126,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0d904b67b8df594c2b717197f91fc5ab789b7fc5","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"呢段時間，相信唔少手足都會思考緊抗爭嘅路要點樣行落去， 我係p牌仔，好歡迎大家俾下意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經過77遊行嘅觀察  <br />\n發現內地遊客其實唔抗拒介紹香港現況嘅傳單(香港人在幹什麼、什麼是返送中 etc) <br />\n有一堆遊客都會喺企度睇 想知我哋發生緊咩事 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">既然遊客唔抗拒接收相關訊息 咁我哋更加應該將香港人嘅聲音＆我哋人抗爭嘅精神輸出</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有人會問:「香港都未搞掂，點解我哋要理內地/其他地方??」<br />\n答案好簡單，因為<strong>中共最驚就喺內地民眾發覺事件嘅真相，最怕人民嘅民主意識開始覺醒</strong> <br />\n唔好忘記，我哋面對嘅唔單指喺淋病， 淋病只係中共管治嘅傀儡，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我哋真正面對嘅喺極權、喺中共</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對抗極權係一場持久戰， 冇一步登天嘅史例，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既然冇得同中共硬碰硬， 咁我哋就要諗方法持久地輸出軟實力</span></span> (搞埋晒D一帶一路講文化、歷史呢D,其實都係軟實力，我哋當然要以其人之道還治其人之身)， 喺思想上薰陶內地民眾， 等佢哋慢慢學識要發聲、要企出嚟爭取權益， 呢啲係建構自由＆民主社會嘅第一步。 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要令內地民眾喺思想上唔再受鉗制、意識到自己可以反抗，呢樣野先喺令中共最棘手嘅!! </span></span><br />\n點解大陸唔俾上Google,YouTube， 睇歐美劇都要翻牆？因為極權管治會滲透喺生活中每一個細節，咁先可以嚴密監控人民嘅思想同埋一舉一動，逼令民眾喺被剝削、不公義嘅情況下都被迫禁聲， 以便管治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">或者我哋可以做嘅就喺<br />\n親自講解俾遊客知香港真正發生緊咩事、 點解要抗爭，等佢哋知道我哋並唔係大陸報導中所講嘅「暴徒」，咁中共點樣封鎖消息、點樣抹黑香港人都無用!!!<br />\n香港好多地區e.g.上水、 尖沙咀、銅鑼灣、東涌、沙田......都有唔少遊客 <br />\n喺各區遍地開花嘅街站＆去發夢嘅手足可以幫幫手，趁機會派下傳單＆同遊客講解下香港人一路以嚟嘅抗爭係為咗啲咩， 亦都可以加入一啲內地市民可能比較熟悉嘅問題( e.g.毒奶粉、 教育、房屋、戶籍、外國網站要翻牆 etc)， 製造機會等佢哋反思下自己現時生存嘅地方係咪有啲嘢好唔妥，而市民理論上有權利發聲。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">唔好咁天真，侈求一兩次就會有成效，依家做嘅喺散播思維嘅種子 。記住記住，呢埸係持久戰！！ 要由思想、文化、教育多路進攻、續漸滲透， 同中共鬥智鬥力鬥長命。</span><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">對抗極權係一條艱辛而漫長嘅路，手足加油！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\np.s.各位手足不如分享下自己嗰區嘅旅客有咩特色"},{"pid":"0a2238f8000e6a57e02276a5d1104925a33b1d73","tid":1293094,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"今鋪真係要封港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61908305a2a09d03f8bd6a7bcb0e3ae6492133f3","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"458ec93bf02485fb6fd0c4003eed301583ccf3c5","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"0e5e1cf75bb45a6b4b95033e8c32f3a568fc10b0","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"f4e993bc726cbf3ffbd265f79f9a1503d7893e00","tid":1293094,"uid":133724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"20a7d5c9a9958caca82fd36834d3d0a08aaeec29","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a62244d9de1d7a1339da531e4facdafe0eab0ab6","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1470b1bec183a8827e155c18393f4e482b55391c","tid":1293094,"uid":257737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"救到香港就得！"},{"pid":"44092113d198ad670267c9ff01adeadba9779da2","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"340bbd0c5bda6f10e14a8f15352caae8295ef9d7","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1470b1bec183a8827e155c18393f4e482b55391c","tid":1293094,"uid":257737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"救到香港就得！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"一定要教！"},{"pid":"8d059ea4fe97f9921da54a01a53ac0905acfef12","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭呀！"},{"pid":"81be4aa9b8479e6893c31d2d2f328f40d19da2bf","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭呀！"},{"pid":"010cdf8bf2d9a589a98e5bf2014510b739567af0","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭呀！"},{"pid":"0d1b30b164a5050f016e15a1d1c595d4ac43d9ca","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭呀！"},{"pid":"19fc8a58734f2488818736b90b891973565009fe","tid":1293094,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"場仗未打完架！五大訴求未接納，一眾被捕士未釋放，林鄭未鞠躬，盧偉聰未落台，外國戰線啱啱先開始(在此向攬炒巴致敬)，現階段邊個同政府對話邊個就係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEbbGfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEbbGfV.jpg&h=252d433f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMfoug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMfoug.jpg&h=5527c394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qANusVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqANusVW.jpg&h=5737c822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QQzD2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QQzD2C.jpg&h=5961c3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0zD2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0zD2D.jpg&h=747e3cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hL0LLHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhL0LLHD.jpg&h=496d3a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZythBPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZythBPj.jpg&h=f98e34dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b267dbf0c0bf8417d5e5e545c7e3137c3905afe0","tid":1293094,"uid":67069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"929cd490aad12ca070f279a9b2d0533054534a21","tid":1293094,"uid":268632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"有無可能係機場派傳單？<br />\n呢個有無問題？<br />\n<br />\n每次50人左右？"},{"pid":"d0ebcd34845b61d10833802c69e50eaae1823f3d","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a2238f8000e6a57e02276a5d1104925a33b1d73","tid":1293094,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"今鋪真係要封港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"就係要佢知道香港人嘅精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1aba6488b1bdf15b89c7840717729ba11b0944","tid":1293094,"uid":40880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"我唔認同要加入大陸城市既情況入我地既訴求入面<br />\n但好支持向唔同既人介紹我地做緊既野，發生緊d咩<br />\n唔洗佢地認同，只要佢地知<br />\n就算佢地番去同人鬧都好，起碼會spread開件事"},{"pid":"d2680fa84a09991b2b0e0a86493a6627245fdad6","tid":1293094,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d0ebcd34845b61d10833802c69e50eaae1823f3d","tid":1293094,"uid":270126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a2238f8000e6a57e02276a5d1104925a33b1d73","tid":1293094,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"今鋪真係要封港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"就係要佢知道香港人嘅精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" c